	<h1>COVID-19 Resources</h1>
		<h4>The Pleasantville Community School District has prepared a COVID-19 Continuous Learning Plan. Information on this program and COVID-19 resources will be placed on this page.</h4>

	  	  	  <p>Pleasantville's continuous learning plan has been approved by the Iowa Department of Education and will begin on Monday, April 13th for all students in grades PK-12. We are excited to partner with students and families in providing engaging and relevant educational experiences during this unprecedented time in education.</p>

<p>Below are links to several different ways to learn more about our continuous learning plan. Patrons have the option to view a short video outlining the plan or read through a slide show presentation and FAQ document on their own.</p>

<p>Please stay in touch with our staff if there is anything we can do to be of service during this time!</p>

